title: Amazing Spider-Man (1999 - 2013)
description: Looking for the one superhero comic you just have to read? You've found it! Amazing Spider-Man is the cornerstone of the Marvel Universe. This is where you'll find all the big-time action, major storylines and iconic Spider-Man magic you'd come to expect from the Wall-Crawler.
